{"tid":1284644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果唔係反共導演李力持，我都唔知中共做埋咁多衰野","createTime":"2019-07-04T08:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T14:17:06.000Z","uid":36797,"like":467,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"f76fd90d5f5a186baa32ca5a82edd4d251cf8e7b","tid":1284644,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktSLpUbRL6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DktSLpUbRL6Y&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=634f4484\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktSLpUbRL6Y</a><br />\n短短五分鐘節錄，句句都係諷刺緊中共統治下既社會風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先係屈盲人偷睇國家機密，之後幾個有關係有武藝既政治犯都過唔到公安嗰關，周星馳竟然一舊水人仔就賄賂得到，串大陸行賄情況串得好入肉<br />\n<br />\n細個對中共有啲咁既風氣真係完全唔知，真係多得李大導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n套戲仲有好多情節諷刺緊大陸<br />\n一，對於中共極力隱瞞既六四事件，喺電影早段已經將關鍵字眼放左出黎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQBZoSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQBZoSh.png&h=22f7cd4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二，當金鎗人開槍，佢要求香琴用手幫掩耳，令香琴只可以掩住自己的單耳，諷刺中國大陸「犧牲自我，讓領導先走」既社會風氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yx1KzZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYx1KzZx.png&h=42ce97ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三，金鎗人偷恐龍頭骨企圖賣出國外，本身已經係貪污，佢仲利用職權嫁禍比人，反映中共官員有幾貪腐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZfO1Fp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZfO1Fp.png&h=5bf9874e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四，對白：「你阿媽係漢奸，你老竇係走狗，你阿爺係賣國賊，你就係漢奸、走狗、賣國賊！」，分明係影射文革時大陸啲批鬥風氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qa5Z8kD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqa5Z8kD.png&h=92783838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諷刺中共既例子真係太多，不能盡錄。<br />\n不得不讚李大導用心，<span style=\"color: red;\">長期接觸佢既反共電影，真係會喚醒年輕人對抗中共既諗法</span>，難怪四十以上中年人多數形容依類戲為低俗無里頭，表示唔理解，反而年輕人世界裡面，佢既電影仍然歷久常新，<span style=\"color: red;\">李力持大導演，成功將革命反共既種子，用電影深深種入年輕人腦海。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKaSJQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKaSJQq.jpg&h=ea3dadb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記得電影中一句對白：「虧你仲有面企喺『忠黨愛國』四個字之前，總之中國一日有你呢個大魔頭，啲老百姓都唔會有好日子過。我今日，一定要做瓜你。」<br />\n對象係邊個？不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkN53Ux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkN53Ux.png&h=43a7e29c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喺局勢最緊張關頭，李大導終於向香港年輕人發出指令<br />\n到底喺李力持大導演既帶領下，行動會升級成點<br />\n好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de750e2efaa86c7c201d49e291847d188ded5a9f","tid":1284644,"uid":36797,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"假如香港成功立國，李力持應記一功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70563cacceeeba6d5d123e2ca28d2d089493614","tid":1284644,"uid":36797,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"比多啲人認識李力持"},{"pid":"e680c242213743e00d64f6ee75f659b40c5b6220","tid":1284644,"uid":11876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a61f67f5c812043f1951dfff63576018fc2ec9","tid":1284644,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacdbb894d692a745eef61c3eb3a484278a54bfa","tid":1284644,"uid":22638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{